Source: pg-text-semver
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/bigsmoke/pg_text_semver

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-text-semver
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-text-semver
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Semantic version domain and comparison operators for PostgreSQL
 pg_text_semver provides a semver domain based on PostgreSQL text plus parsing,
 comparison functions, casts, and operators for working with Semantic
 Versioning 2.0.0 values inside SQL.
